      "file_path": "boot/dcae2_vm_init.sh",
      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 170,
      "message": "There will be 2 seperate cloud region: cloud region for pod25, and cloud region for pod25dns . There is no guarantee that these two region are with the same name. So I would suggest cloud region for pod25dns use the value provided by 'dnsaas_region'\nSuggest change: CLOUD_REGION=\"$(cat /opt/config/dnsaas_region.txt)\"",
