      "message": "No, actually, you can choose one of following:\n\"{\\\"tenant_name\\\": \\\"${DNSAAS_TENANT_NAME}\\\"}\"\nor\n\"{\\\"auth\\\":{\\\"tenantName\\\": \\\"${DNSAAS_TENANT_NAME}\\\"}}\"\nBut I suggest you follow the latter one since it is standard Keystone V2.0 api request format.",
